entry.title: About Me
entry.summary: My name is Sophie Lancaster and I am originally from Warsaw, Indiana. I am a junior at the University of Notre Dame studying Computer Science with the intent to minor in Engineering Corporate Practice. I have spent a summer researching machine learning in Budapest, Hungary.
